    {\displaystyle B_{i}\subset M}
  , 
  
    
      
        i
        =
        1
        ,
        …
        ,
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle i=1,\ldots ,n}
  , such that their boundaries are smooth submanifolds of codimension one. Let 

  
    
      
        B
        =
        M
         
        (
        
          ⋃
          
            i
            =
            1
          
          
            n
          
        
        Int
        ⁡
        (
        
          B
          
            i
          
        
        )
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle B=M\ (\bigcup _{i=1}^{n}\operatorname {Int} (B_{i}))}
  , where 
  
    
      
        Int
        ⁡
        (
        
          B
          
            i
          
        
