            m
            n
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \int _{\Omega }{\overline {\psi _{m}}}(q)\psi _{n}(q)\,dq=\delta _{mn}}
  Curiously, the free-field Schrödinger equation is the same as the Helmholtz equation,

  
    
      
        
          (
          
            
              ∇
              
                2
              
            
